WEBVTT

00:02.800 --> 00:05.394
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:08.360 --> 00:10.430
- Carla, give me a beer.
- Right.

00:11.680 --> 00:13.989
What's the story with Sam?
Isn't he back from ltaly yet?

00:14.160 --> 00:17.152
No. Three whole days,
and we haven't heard a word.

00:17.320 --> 00:19.959
He just went there to stop Diane
and Frasier from getting married.

00:20.120 --> 00:22.031
Don't know what could
be taking him so long.

00:22.200 --> 00:24.509
Maybe Frasier's still thanking him.

00:25.200 --> 00:28.636
I wouldn't be a bit surprised if Diane
now had a "Malone" after her name.

00:29.160 --> 00:30.434
Well, could be, Cliffie.

00:30.600 --> 00:33.034
That ltaly's an awfully darn
romantic place.

00:33.200 --> 00:35.111
I almost went there myself
on my honeymoon.

00:35.280 --> 00:38.955
Had the plane reservations
and the hotel reservations. Everything.

00:39.120 --> 00:40.553
Well, what stopped you, Norm?

00:40.720 --> 00:43.712
Oh, Vera.
You know, she insisted on coming.

00:45.000 --> 00:51.074
